Love,
I can’t really express how much this relationship has opened my eyes and shown me my life was messing a part of me that was very important. You introduced me to God brought me to HIM. Changed my perspective on my things I used to look over, running away from my self in situations I didn’t fully understand. I am grateful for you and the loving powerful woman you are! A beautiful loving mother to our kids. Seeing how you can get deeper into my kids souls and touching their hearts and feelings that is astonishing and I’m happy it is you! We became friends before we were anything and it was so real that the feelings was mutual our minds were mutual and the beginning came. I want this love forever with you! You push me and you stand by me you see me you acknowledge me and you love me! For you I will go that extra mile! I love you baby!! Thank you! @mom.e.ana
